invalid type: string "Recommendations for Q1 2025\n\nBased on Q4 performance, we propose the following strategies for Q1 2025:\n\nEnhance Conversion Optimization: Invest in advanced A/B testing and user experience improvements to achieve the 15.0% conversion rate target.\n\nExpand B2B Efforts: Increase ABM budget by 10% to target additional enterprise verticals, such as manufacturing and retail.\n